    • resolveCAMsMenu

      static application.SessionStatus resolveCAMsMenu(Staff staff, int choice, String argument, List<User> userList, List<Camp> campList, List<Signup> signupList, List<Enquiry> enquiryList, List<Suggestion> suggestionList)
      Method to determine functionality for each choice, defined for Staff exclusively.
      Parameters:
      staff - Staff user working the menus
      choice - Input integer choice for menu
      argument - Any additional string arguments (used for Camp filters)
      userList - List of all User objects. Passed to other classes.
      campList - List of all Camp objects. Passed to other classes.
      signupList - List of all Signup objects. Passed to other classes.
      enquiryList - List of all Enquiry objects. Passed to other classes.
      suggestionList - List of all Suggestion objects. Passed to other classes.

      SessionStatus to determine which state CAMs should continue with
